           " fires 'target', if two are connected it fires 'target2', and so o"
           "n."$0A"If 'Less Or Equal' is set, fires all targetnames UP TO the "
           "current player count (so with four players connected, all four tar"
           "gets would fire instead of just target4)."$0A"If 'Two Players Per'"
           " is set, requires double the number of players for each threshhold"
           " (for scaling up to 8 players)."$0A
        }
        target_screenshake:e =
